#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - by int - int by int
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"multipleOf": 2}
--- json
10


=== Test 2 - by int - int by int fail
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
7


=== Test 3 - by int - ignores non-numbers
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"foo"


=== Test 4 - by number - zero is multiple of anything
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"multipleOf": 1.5}
--- json
0


=== Test 5 - by number - 4.5 is multiple of 1.5
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
4.5


=== Test 6 - by number - 35 is not multiple of 1.5
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
35


=== Test 7 - by small number - 0.0075 is multiple of 0.0001
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"multipleOf": 0.0001}
--- json
0.0075


=== Test 8 - by small number - 0.00751 is not multiple of 0.0001
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
0.00751


